    title: 'Ship AI features without building infrastructure',
    description: 'Atmosphere handles streaming text delivery, tool execution, RAG context injection, and guardrails. You plug in your model — we deliver the output to the browser.',
    detail: `<p>Atmosphere provides the <strong>server-to-browser transport layer</strong> for AI applications while your model framework handles inference.</p>
